toAster Desktop Analytics for R works with Teradata Aster Big Data database.

Package brings access to Aster database and its powerful SQL/MR functions to
R desktop to help visualize and analyze with Aster powerful map-reduce
functions (SQL/MR).
 
Aster database is SQL Map-Reduce MPP database offering transparent distributed 
and parallel environement, SQL compliance, and variety of statistical and 
machine learning functions implemented in native SQL distributed datastore.

With toaster you utilize processing power of Aster and descriptive power of 
R language while analyzing data with visualilzations. Graphical functions use 
ggplot2 functions and are adjusted for data produced with Aster functions.
